      <title>美国码头工人罢工：衡量经济成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/us-dockworker-s-strike-measuring-the-economic-cost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，美国东海岸和墨西哥湾沿岸各大港口的码头工人因未能就新合同达成一致而罢工，这是近 50 年来首次。彭博经济的 Anna Wong 在彭博电视台上分析了此次罢工对美国经济的潜在影响。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/us-dockworker-s-strike-measuring-the-economic-cost</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:28:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
