      <title>阿波罗首席执行官罗文警告称，大幅降息可能会适得其反</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/apollo-ceo-rowan-warns-that-aggressive-rate-cuts-could-backfire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司首席执行官马克·罗文表示，他认为美联储目前没有理由继续降息来刺激经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/apollo-ceo-rowan-warns-that-aggressive-rate-cuts-could-backfire</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:18:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿波罗首席执行官罗文谈私募市场贷款、选举、美联储利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/in-full-rowan-on-private-market-lending-election-fed-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿波罗全球管理公司首席执行官马克·罗文讨论了私募市场贷款、阿波罗与花旗集团合作后可能出现的更多银行合作以及私募股权与公募股权的前景。在与彭博社乔纳森·费罗的对话中，他还对美国总统大选和美联储政策前景发表了评论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-02/in-full-rowan-on-private-market-lending-election-fed-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:11:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利央行在福林贬值后承诺实施“有限”绿色计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hungarian-central-bank-pledges-limited-green-program-after-forint-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利央行承诺维持“严谨而紧缩”的货币政策，以缓解投资者的担忧，因为福林跌至一年半以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/hungarian-central-bank-pledges-limited-green-program-after-forint-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Oct 2024 13:08:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
