      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-02/poland-leaves-rates-steady-again-as-inflation-accelerates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在通胀率升至超出央行容忍范围后，波兰将利率稳定期延长至一年。]]></description>
